# # EXTEND ANNOTATION TABLE TO DOCUMENT RENAMING for later reference, including genes that have no orthologue in humans----

# replace "" with NA to assign missings in ensembl ata

  gene_anno[,(i) := ifelse(get(i) =="", NA, get(i))]
